description: Here at Livin' Lite AZ we serve deliciously different, free-range, organic pulled chicken sandwiches, veggie burgers made with Ramona Farms Tepary Beans, fresh, organic salads, soups and more! We use all organic and all-natural ingredients, locally sourced whenever possible. Everyone will enjoy our rotating menu, including gluten free and vegan options!Livin' Lite AZ also does things a bit differently than other food trucks. We count calories! Not only calories but protein, carbs, fat, sugar...you get the idea! You can check out our website www.LivinLiteAZ.com for the nutritional information and an ingredient list for our menu items so that you can maintain a healthy lifestyle!
name: Livin' Lite AZ
